data.description: **Please call Arlene Gonnella at 201-306-1357 for a private showing of this incredible home. By Appointment only!** Spectacular Georgian Colonial Estate reminiscent of "Gone with the Wind" totally self sufficient on 65 acres with pond, greenhouse with organic gardens and orchards! Drive up one mile driveway to home of your dreams with massive columns, 12' high ceilings on the 1st floor and substantial moldings. Radiant heated floors on first floor and lower level. Stunning gourmet eat in kitchen totally open to family room with access to soon to be completed breathtaking indoor pool! Office overlooking beautiful property. Luxurious master suite with massive custom closets and spa-like master bath. Three other bedroom suites on second floor. The third floor is absolutely enchanting with rooms replicating your favorite childhood memories! Lower level has beautiful media room, huge walk-in wine cellar, game room and more..Must see!!
